Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ON THIS BOND
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Dai, the Hero is the only one\Nwho can defeat the Dark King,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the only one who can unlock\NDai's full potential...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one who has been with him\Nsince the very beginning of this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp... That's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Work together... and achieve victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, please watch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll get the Dark King for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!\NBan's going to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and ready yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban will never attack first\Nin that stance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the Demonic Guard of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that sort of skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ultimate defensive skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, it's for countering.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While it lets him use\Nthree skills at once,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,used offensively,\Nit's just a triple attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ban's skills are great enough\Nto defeat most enemies without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet the Tenchimato
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is a stance Ban only uses\Nagainst truly powerful enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By letting an enemy attack first,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he can hit them with his super skills\Nof attack, defense, and magic,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}completely obliterating them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unbeatable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But he must charge a massive amount\Nof energy in order to unleash these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not normal attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitting his opponent\Nwith these three super attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is what brings such devastation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That immovable stance isn't\Njust to make his enemies attack first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably lets him conserve energy,\Nstoring it in his body
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and then unleashing it all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears Aban's parting words\Nweren't said out of desperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A fledgling like you\Nsaw through my ultimate skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But, knowing that, what can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you intend to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I take this stance, it's over.\NNo one can break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And buying time is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's wounds were inflicted by Dark Aura\Nand can't be healed by healing spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the problem!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai's not healing at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can only think of\None way to attack Ban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hit him in the brief moments\Nfollowing an attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before he charges for the next.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But with everyone in this state...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can always initiate\Nan attack as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-He dropped his stance!\N-Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Larhart! Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to ask this\Nfrom complete strangers, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,give your lives to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They say ancient humans thought thunder\Nwas the gods fighting in the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can feel the terrifying power\Nfrom way down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai and the others must be fighting\NDark King Ban right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unbelievable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no ifs or buts about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Either the Dark King falls,\Nor the Surface World ends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's one or the other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on a whole different level!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please just stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can almost hear the anguished cries\Nof your friends, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They might as well have stayed behind\Nand left you here with the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This game...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-D-Darn it!\N-It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for my plan.\NIt looks like it was worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked us to give our lives to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's any hope of winning,\Ntell us what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We've reached our limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't hold out, then all is lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My plan wasn't anything complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what you said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a shield for Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all beat to hell here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us can face Ban directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted the three of us\Nto take his blows and create an opening,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing Dai to focus on the offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wanted"? You're talking past tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I underestimated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we won't even be able to\Ntake more blows for Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall end this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wipe you all out\Nwith my Calamity Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like some poor little Eyes\Nwill be disintegrated as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He means me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make this one move slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can enjoy your fear longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Calamity Wall!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! He's laughing his head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll survive this Calamity Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point if we can't withstand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I need him to use\Nthat ultimate skill one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! Didn't you see\Nthe three of us fail against it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Demonic Guard of Heaven and Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,can't be beaten head-on,\Nnot even with ten people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But the moment he unleashes that ultimate\Nskill is when he's most vulnerable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, you had the same idea as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was the only way, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Withstand all three super attacks\Nand then attack immediately after!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way\Nto defeat that unbeatable skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I knew that it would kill me\Nif I tried it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So you saw through it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice going, partner. That settles it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not alone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got allies here who will suffer\Nthose super attacks in your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means getting hit by all three,\NI'll give you the chance to strike back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that was the plan.\NThese guys are crazy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an impossibility\Nwithin an impossibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And we haven't even gotten him\Nto take his ultimate stance yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,First we need to take care of\Nthe big problem at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still a gamble whether\Nthe Dark King will take his stance or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Little Hym!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count me in\Non that hopeless gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly, I don't think\NI'll be able to see how it turns out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gained my respect\Nfor the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:11:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't let you beat me\Nin terms of dedication to Master Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way is Ban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-You can have it!\N-My life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Larhart! Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They actually did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.56,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4}AURA KNUCKLE{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}HAKENDISUTORU{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this condition\NI doubt anything I do will work on him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll be living bullets!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll use our bodies as weapons\Nand charge him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you're prepared to die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their intensity...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No simple attack can counter them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Tenchimato!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Medoroa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Phoenix Wing!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You surprised me, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did you once again\Nforce me to take this stance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but by using a delayed Medoroa,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you even managed to scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But, unfortunately for you,\Nyou're now out of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? I can't drop my stance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something inside of me senses a threat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do they still...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym, Larhart, thank you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You used to be our enemies,\Nand yet you've done so much for us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've given us a chance at victory!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't waste it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your final attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that, Mister Dark King?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This final attack we're about to unleash
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,will break through your precious\NTenchimato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gigastrash and Medoroa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know that\Nyour most powerful attacks won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it, Ban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp didn't cast Medoroa\Nto try to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it to show me the perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after you use Tenchimato,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a slight delay\Nuntil you're ready to counter again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast Medoroa in order for\NDai and I to see the timing for ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just as I thought,\Nyou froze for an instant!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And on top of that, you couldn't properly\Ndeflect the Medoroa back at me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though Mystban could do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nif we strike at that timing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,even wounded as we are,\Nwe have a chance at a comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's the reason why I froze.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you never knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tenchimato has never failed to \Nbeat your enemy, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenchimato is my ultimate skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To use it means to\Nabsolutely erase any enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you have that weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Being your greatest and final skill\Ncauses that opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how great a skill it is,\Nyou shouldn't show it off so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to secure a victory,\Nyou should attack normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Dark King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a gamble!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With their stamina drained, having Ban\Nattack normally would be worse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pop is purposely provoking Ban\Nto get him to use his ultimate skill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's betting on the Dark King's\Nabsolute confidence in his ultimate skill!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept that challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes! Now it's all or nothing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm interested in seeing if that\Nlittle provocation of yours pays off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined\Nthat I had such a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But first...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there were two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai! Popp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is grim!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know what Popp's planning,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but those two are too wounded\Nto break Ban's ultimate skill!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! I can't even be a shield for them\Nin their moment of need!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I see, Dai doesn't have\Nthe stamina to use Gigastrash anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you plan to finish things\Nwith your Medoroa, I can deflect it again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,whether back at you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither attack can be used to finish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you two can possibly\Npull off that plan by yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even withstand\Nmy ultimate skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you intend to hit me\Nwith a deciding blow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I must see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of us will use the deciding blow?\NIsn't it obvious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hero is the one\Nwho always defeats the Dark King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the shield\Nagainst your ultimate skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember Mentor once used\Ntwo spells at the same time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought maybe I could pull it off now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very talented, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be better than a single Medoroa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but I thought you were smarter than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you do simple math?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's assume that Explosion-type spell\Nis as strong as a Ionazun spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And that you can cause\Na great deal of damage
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with the rest of your Magic Power\Nfocused in that staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That adds up to two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about my third attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If a frail human like you\Ntakes a direct hit unguarded,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't even serve as a shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, I'll deflect your spell\Nwith my Phoenix Wing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll shatter your weapon\Nwith my Calamity End.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That'll leave you defenseless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you'll be hit by the combined force of\Nthe deflected spell and my Kaiser Phoenix.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be incinerated in an instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and Dai will be hit by my spell\Nbefore he can exploit any weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll both be reduced to ashes.\NThat's how it will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Things might be different\Nif you only had a few more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet... you still try.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp may have been\Na little unreliable at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's been with me in this battle\Nsince the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a friend I trust.\NHe's saved me time and time again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If Popp says he'll make\Nan opening for me, then he will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is trust him\Nand focus my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You should remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have started\Nthis adventure together,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but we've met numerous people\Non our way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We've fought against\Nand been saved by them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If even one of them hadn't been there,\Nwe wouldn't be facing you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they're far away,\Neven if they can't move,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we're all connected\Nby the bond of our souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the strength of this bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see it,\Nbut I know it's gonna surprise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it once.\NDon't make me say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't kill me with your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Tenchimato!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good! It's just as Ban said!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Mirror of Shahal?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:17.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:28.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:36.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:45.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:49.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:56.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:02.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:09.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:15.08,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:20.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:27.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to the desperate charge\Nby Hym and Larhart, Popp found a way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp reflects Ban's magic\Nwith the Mirror of Shahal,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}consuming Ban in flames.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Using the chance that everyone has\Ngiven him, Dai readies a desperate attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Greatest, Final Comeback"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:23:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.33,0:24:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,
